  "faqs": [
    {
      "question": "What is the warranty period?",
      "answer": "All Tata passenger vehicles come with a standard 3-year / 1,00,000 km warranty (whichever comes first). You can extend it to 5 years / 1,50,000 km with our Extended Warranty plan at just ₹12,999.",
      "tags": ["warranty", "guarantee", "coverage", "years", "extend"]
    },
    {
      "question": "Do you offer financing / EMI options?",
      "answer": "Yes! We partner with SBI, HDFC Bank, ICICI Bank, and Axis Bank. Interest rates start from 8.5% p.a. For example, the Nexon Smart+ at ₹8.00L can be financed at just ₹13,499/month EMI with a 20% down payment over 5 years.",
      "tags": ["finance", "emi", "loan", "bank", "payment", "monthly", "interest", "down payment"]
    },
    {
      "question": "What is the delivery time?",
      "answer": "Current delivery timelines: Nexon — 2 to 4 weeks depending on variant and color. Exact availability can be confirmed at the showroom.",
      "tags": ["delivery", "waiting", "time", "when", "how long", "availability", "stock"]
    },
    {
      "question": "What colors are available?",
      "answer": "The Nexon comes in exciting colors including Fearless Purple, Creative Ocean, Flame Red, Daytona Grey, Pure Grey, and the exclusive Grasslands Beige.",
      "tags": ["color", "colour", "shade", "available", "options", "paint"]
    },
    {
      "question": "What is the service schedule?",
      "answer": "Service intervals are every 6 months or 7,500 km. The first 3 services cost approximately ₹3,500 to ₹5,500 depending on the model. We also offer a Tata Service Value Pack starting at ₹14,999 covering 5 years of maintenance.",
      "tags": ["service", "maintenance", "cost", "schedule", "interval", "free service", "after sales", "review", "mixed review"]
    },
    {
      "question": "Is there a test drive available?",
      "answer": "Absolutely! We offer both showroom test drives and home test drives. You can book a test drive instantly — weekend slots fill up quickly, so I recommend booking today.",
      "tags": ["test drive", "try", "drive", "experience", "demo", "book"]
    },
    {
      "question": "What about resale value?",
      "answer": "Tata vehicles have seen a significant jump in resale values. The Nexon retains approximately 60-65% of its value after 3 years, which is the highest in the compact SUV segment.",
      "tags": ["resale", "value", "sell", "second hand", "depreciation", "retain"]
    },
    {
      "question": "Do you offer exchange/trade-in?",
      "answer": "Yes, we have the Tata Exchange program. Bring any brand's used car and we'll give you the best valuation. Exchange customers get an additional ₹15,000 to ₹25,000 exchange bonus depending on the model.",
